Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Several days have passed since that incident.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nii-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm in love with someone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, like always,\NI'm making a meal for my younger sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, I'm leaving it here,\Nso make sure to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, wait!\NI have something important to talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, so please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hold on. Let me get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's with that outfit!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-It's not weird, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:01:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-Don't stare at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-Why did you suddenly\Nwant to wear clothes like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't get it?\NAfter making me read something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,W-Well, after reading something like that,\NI can understand you'd be cautious around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to be your older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Romance between siblings\Nis out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-How does it end up that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The other day, when I said "I was in love..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:03:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. That means\N"you can't answer to my feelings", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I totally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, what is this "something important"\Nyou want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want you to make\Na project proposal with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Project proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. To turn the new piece\NI wrote the other day into a book,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I first have to submit a project proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If it gets turned down,\NI won't be able to turn it into a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What we want to turn into a book\Nis that manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Got it. But what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've already decided what I want you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want you to draw illustrations\Nof a lewd younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Honestly! You're such a pervert, Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me to draw illustrations\Nof a lewd younger sister!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because the heroine for my piece\Nis a younger sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and you're good at drawing lewd art,\Nso that's why I requested that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Liar! I'm sure\Nthere's a perverted reason behind this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you fixated on that thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because... Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You said you love me, right, Nii?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So much that you'd fall in love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, that's only as an older brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd never have lewd thoughts\Nabout my younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's with that look on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Geez.
