Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.47,RightSign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(490.25,207.111)\frz22.2}Save me! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.39,RightSign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\frz30.51\pos(446.584,201.778)}{\i1}What are you doing? Hurry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For now, I took my own image\Nand made it into a drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Does the heroine look something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Something is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you draw her a bit cuter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cuter? In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Someone that looks more like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There you go saying stuff like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:08:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Asking me to draw a "lewd illustration" of a\N"younger sister like me"? Such sexual harassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The ideal heroine is exactly like you,\Nso I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-You say exactly like me but,\Nyou have to be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A bit more phantasmal, like a fairy or an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So that's the image...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And make her face a bit younger,\Nand with smaller breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And, I want you to change\Nthe nature of its eroticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A kid with not much sex appeal,\Nbut when you notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the hem on her clothes are turned up,\Nshowing her thighs,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and you can't help your racing heart,\Nkind of eroticism...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes! Exactly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, stop th—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come save me right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I saved you in the end, so don't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R-Right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, you had to escape right away?\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-They showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"They"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The editors from Full-Drive Publishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They're going to monitor me\Nto see if I'm properly working or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, Yamada Elf-sensei,\Nlet's go home and work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune-sensei, I beg you! Shelter me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Anything. I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You just said you'll do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Teach me how to write a project proposal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:10:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh no! You're so unfair!\NSuch a raunchy request to my noble self...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Me, a super-pretty girl,\Nis saying she'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You think such a request is going to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Shut up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And "Hurry back up".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to meet Eromanga-sensei, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yo, it's the first time seeing you like this, huh,\NYamada Elf-sensei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eromanga-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I don't know anyone by that name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She says she's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's like a pet phrase of hers,\Nso don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way! Elf-sensei is super cute\Nwhen you see her up close!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, hey, what kind of panties\Nare you wearing right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-Why would you start off\Nwith that question?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I call you Elf-chan?\NIs that your real name? How old are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you started wearing a bra already?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What? It's the Eromanga-sensei\Nthat you've been wanting to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Her behavior is like some lewd old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I different from what you imagined?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, it matches your penname\Nso well that I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After reading "that manuscript", her personality\Nis completely different from this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-Nii-san,\Nyou showed that manuscript to her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I read it, and I've heard much about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It must have been something for you to read\Nsuch a passionate love-letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you know that much. I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course! We're like buddies now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, we're not—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You carried me like a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's how we called each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop altering memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So you guys get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't matter who Izumi-sensei\Nis all lovey-dovey with!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, weren't you going to teach us\Nhow to write a project proposal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R-Right! A project proposal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, you mentioned something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But for things like that, you can just\Nwrite something in five minutes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, you feel like you've done some real work,\Nand concentrate on playing games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And that's why the editorial staff\Nstarted monitoring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's totally not just me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Everyone totally procrastinates\Nand plays games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No way that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, so, talk of a project proposal is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Say, you like games, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You had a lot of consoles in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's play a match! A match!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sheesh, why am I sent out\Nto go buy snacks for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I haven't even played games\Nwith my younger sister yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Wh-Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I-I-I was just showing my panties\Nto Eromanga-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}What kind of erotic play is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}It can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}She said she'd draw me an illustration\Nif I showed her my panties, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I wanted to see panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}If that settled things,\Nwe wouldn't need the police!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}When I see a cute girl,\NI can't help but want to see her panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}That's how all illustrators are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Apologize! Apologize right now\Nto all the illustrators in the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You see now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That raunchy pose was also specified by\NEromanga-sensei, so don't get any wrong ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, the next time I draw nudes for\NYamada-sensei, I can draw them better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You guys make a better team than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You sold me out, Masamune!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}- I don't wanna work! I'm gonna play games!\N- Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Sagiri. What kind of conversation did you\Nhave with her while I was out shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, nothing much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, what do you think of Elf?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A weird person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, nothing. Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe we should invite her over again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I could write novels easily,\Nbut project proposals...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:10.10,OnTop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(232.817,83.889)}From: Kagurazaka Ayame\NSubject: Got your new piece yet?\NTo: Izumi Masamune
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:14.41,OnTop - Copy,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(634.234,68)}From: Kagurazaka Ayame \N\NSubject: Got your new piece yet?\N\NTo: Izumi Masamune
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:14.41,OnTop - Copy,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(289.233,390.222)}I'll secure a publishing spot,\Nand be waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Secure a publishing spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So if the proposal goes through,\NI can publish it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, this is from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The lewd wrinkles in her panties,\Nand her expression of embarrassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought I drew it really well,\Nso I wanted to boast to you, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, we'll put her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll have this girl show up in my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,An idea came to me seeing this illustration...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can write an amazing scene with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, can you draw\Nmore illustrations like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you draw illustrations\Nthat you feel passionate about,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,new ideas might spark up, like just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Will you draw for me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm counting on you,\NEromanga-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I don't know anyone by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A serious problem has occurred.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't draw anything but loli girls now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That is indeed a serious problem. But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought you practiced\Nand can draw big-chested girls, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I drew those watching videos and idols on TV.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And that's not good enough now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, I need light bulbs flashing like\Nwhen I saw Elf-chan to get any inspiration.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Light bulbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm desperately trying to think of a way\Nto see panties in real life, up close,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}without leaving my room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In any case!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see girls other than Elf-chan,\Nso I can get inspired!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I can draw illustrations that will\Nmake Izumi-sensei conjure up new heroines!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nii-san, do you know someone who's cute,\Nwell-endowed, and willing to show her panties?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over 14.5 million total copies in print,\Na smash hit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The youngest yet\Nsuper-popular author Senju Muramasa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}brings you volume 11 of\N"Legend of the Illusionary Demon Sword."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The anime version is on air right now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:17:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hi, hi! It's everyone's favorite Megumin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...taking a bath!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh, huh, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Onii-san, did you actually imagine something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you want?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How is Izumi-chan since we last spoke?\NHas she come out of her room yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But she seems to have made a friend recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait! I want details!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How's that? Isn't it amazing progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um, can I be honest?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So frustrating!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to be her very first friend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, can I be honest here, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was frustrated, too. It felt like\Nsomeone got ahead of me, just like you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We're comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Onii-san, can we meet right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to consult you about my plan\Nto become friends with Izumi-chan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's it. Sure, where should I head to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you know Takasago Books\Nacross from the train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:56.78,DefaultLow,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\frz6.439\pos(477.001,11.111)}Tomoe's\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NRecommendation Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I arrived a bit too early.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What kind of books are you looking for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Give me a heroine where Eromanga-sensei's\Nlight bulbs will start flashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Like Shana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shut up, shut up, shut up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Or Taiga-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You stupid dog.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Or Maisel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love seeing tall people grovel like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Those are heroines\Nwhere my light bulbs would flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So in other words, you're searching\Nfor a pretty girl with big breasts
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,who can provide inspiration\Nfor Eromanga-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, that puts me in a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you the one who's blushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is about you wanting to use me\Nas a model for your new title, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're gonna go along with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, can you hop onto Skype\Nand show Eromanga-sensei your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's an easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, of course I can't do anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Guess who?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Must be Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Umm, Izumi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh? She found you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Makes sense. I had the calendar on the wall.\NAnd my penname is the same as my real name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, let's get to discussing my plan\Nto become friends with Izumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, right. We were going to talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Onii-san, you write novels, right?\NThe ones that have illustrations...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, I think Izumi-chan\Nlikes stuff like that, too.
