Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, she does have quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So that's why I'm thinking about\Nreading these creepy otaku novels!
